# Study Docs Sync Check

When working on the `study/architecture-analysis` branch or editing files in `docs/study/`:

## On Session Start

1. Run `git fetch origin` and `git log --oneline HEAD..origin/main` to check for upstream changes
2. If there are new commits, run `git diff HEAD..origin/main --stat` to see which files changed
3. Cross-reference changed files against the source code reference mapping below
4. If any referenced source files changed, rebase and update the affected docs
5. After updating, commit with message format: `docs: update study docs for upstream changes`

