## Update Criteria

Only update docs when:
- **API changes**: Function signatures, type definitions, or class structures changed
- **Behavioral changes**: Logic flow, algorithm, or feature behavior changed
- **New features**: New env vars, new options, new capabilities added
- **Line number shifts**: Source code references (`> **源码**:` lines) have incorrect line numbers

Skip updates when:
- Only internal implementation details changed (no API/behavior impact)
- Only tests, comments, or formatting changed
- Only `models.generated.ts` or changelog files changed
